Class TetrominoSpawner

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.TetrominoSpawner

  • public class TetrominoSpawner
extends java.lang.Object
    Class managing the part of the game where a new tetromino has to be spawned at the top of the grid and has to be moved gradually down the grid.
    Author:
    £ukasz Piekarski [wookashp98@gmail.com]
